<%- include ('partials/header') -%>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/first.css">

<div class="position-relative overflow-hidden p-3 p-md-5 m-md-3 text-center ">
    <div class="col-md-5 p-lg-5 mx-auto my-5">
        <h1 class="display-4 fw-normal">Helping Hands</h1>
        <p class="lead fw-normal">In this current period where people have lost there jobs and many people are not able
            to
            get food treatment medicine and basic requirements we created a website to gather everyone and help others
            in this
            good cause</p>
        <a href="/signUp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline-secondary" href="#">Sign
            Up</a>
    </div>
    <div class="product-device shadow-sm d-none d-md-block"></div>
    <div class="product-device product-device-2 shadow-sm d-none d-md-block"></div>
</div>



<div class="uk-child-width-1-3@m" uk-grid>
    <a href="/covid" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <div>
            <div class="uk-card uk-card-hover uk-card-default">
                <div class="uk-card-media-top">
                    <img src="resources/f6.jpeg" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="uk-card-body">
                    <h3 class="uk-card-title">COVID-19 Stats</h3>
                    <p>Your one stop destination for all the related updates regarding COVID-19. The Weekly
                        Epidemiological Update provides an overview of the global, regional and country-level COVID-19
                        cases and deaths, highlighting key data and trends; as well as other pertinent epidemiological
                        information concerning the COVID-19 pandemic.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </a>
    <a href="/food">
        <div>
            <div class="uk-card  uk-card-hover  uk-card-default">
                <div class="uk-card-media-top">
                    <img src="resources/f1.jpeg" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="uk-card-body">
                    <h3 class="uk-card-title">Covid Oriented Food Delivery</h3>
                    <p>The Pandemic has taken a toll on all of us. While some of us are safe and sound, others are still
                        fighting this deadly virus. Being bedridden and with the weakness associated with the illness
                        can be a real challenging task to prepare food. We strive to overcome this difficulty by
                        creating a network between NGOs and independent donors who wish to donate food for the presently
                        infected, self-quarantined patients.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </a>
    <a href="/medicine" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <div>
            <div class="uk-card uk-card-hover uk-card-default">
                <div class="">
                    <img src="resources/f2.jpeg" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="uk-card-body">
                    <h3 class="uk-card-title">Supply of Medicines</h3>
                    <p>Going outdoor to buy medicines, waiting for your turn at the pharmacy, sacrificing your ideal
                        social distancing policies can be a tedious task for many, especially not knowing whether or not
                        the pharmacy has the medicine you require. We collaborated with some of the pharmacies, updated
                        their databases, and made it easy for anyone to check and order their medications..</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </a>


</div>

<br>
<br>
<br>
<div class="uk-child-width-1-3@m" uk-grid>


    <a href="/doctor" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <div>
            <div class="uk-card uk-card-hover uk-card-default">
                <div class="uk-card-media-top">
                    <img src="resources/f3.jpg" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="uk-card-body">
                    <h3 class="uk-card-title">Consultation</h3>
                    <p>Consulting an expert is always a better option than trusting other online resources. We contacted
                        some of the doctors and requested them to allocate some time for online consultation. We created
                        a database of doctors, sorting them according to their specializations and mentioning their
                        consultation hours.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </a>



    <a href="/donation" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <div>
            <div class="uk-card uk-card-hover uk-card-default">
                <div class="uk-card-media-top">
                    <img src="resources/f5.jpeg" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="uk-card-body">
                    <h3 class="uk-card-title">Donate</h3>
                    <p> To operate such an organization, we need the proper support of volunteers and some financial
                        support. Apart from being funded by NGOs and philanthropists, we welcome anyone willing to
                        donate any amount of money. The money donated would be used constructively for the welfare of
                        society.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/oxy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <div>
            <div class="uk-card  uk-card-hover  uk-card-default">
                <div class="uk-card-media-top">
                    <img src="resources/f4.jpeg" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="uk-card-body">
                    <h3 class="uk-card-title">Covid Resources</h3>
                    <p>Resources to all that one might need in a situation of emergency (Oxygen cylinders , bed
                        ,Ventilators,Plasma )
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </a>


</div>

<div class="container col-xl-10 col-xxl-8 px-4 py-5 mb-0 pb-0">
    <div class="row align-items-center g-lg-5 py-5">
        <div class="col-lg-7 text-center text-lg-start">
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold lh-1 mb-3"> Login form</h1>
            <p class="col-lg-10 fs-4">On Login in you can access the above section and use the supplied aid
                provided by shop owners hospitals and doctors</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-10 mx-auto col-lg-5">
            <form class="p-4 p-md-5 border rounded-3 bg-light">
                <div class="form-floating mb-3">
                    <input type="email" class="form-control" id="floatingInput" placeholder="name@example.com">
                    <label for="floatingInput">Email address</label>
                </div>
                <div class="form-floating mb-3">
                    <input type="password" class="form-control" id="floatingPassword" placeholder="Password">
                    <label for="floatingPassword">Password</label>
                </div>
                <div class="checkbox mb-3">
                    <label>
                        <input type="checkbox" value="remember-me"> Remember me
                    </label>
                </div>
                <button class="w-100 btn btn-lg btn-primary" type="submit">Log In</button>
                <hr class="my-4">
                <small class="text-muted">By clicking Log in, you agree to the terms of use.</small>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<%- include ('partials/footer') -%>
